<pb n="0778a" xml:id="T20.1178.0778a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0778a01" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0778a02" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 1178</cb:docNumber>
<lb n="0778a03" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><note n="0778001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】三十帖策子第二十六，【甲】黃檗版淨嚴等校訂加筆本</note><cb:jhead>文殊<note n="0778002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔菩薩〕－【甲】</note><note n="0778002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">菩薩【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0778002"><lem wit="【大】">菩薩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>獻佛陀羅尼名<note n="0778003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">烏＝鳥【甲】</note><note n="0778003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">烏【大】，鳥【甲】</note><app n="0778003"><lem wit="【大】">烏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">鳥</rdg></app>蘇
<lb n="0778a04" ed="T"/>吒<note place="inline">此云滅婬<note n="0778004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">慾＝欲【甲】＊</note><note n="0778004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">慾【大】＊，欲【甲】＊</note><app n="0778004"><lem wit="【大】">慾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">欲</rdg></app>却我慢</note></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0778a05" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0778a06" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT20p0778a0601">時佛勅阿難。為未來沒苦眾生。廣宣流布。時
<lb n="0778a07" ed="T"/>文殊菩薩先說偈言。</p>
<lb n="0778a08" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0778a0801"><l>一切眾生類</l><l>迴<note n="0778005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">沒＝波【甲】</note><note n="0778005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">沒【大】，波【甲】</note><app n="0778005"><lem wit="【大】">沒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">波</rdg></app>婬鬼界</l>
<lb n="0778a09" ed="T"/><l>無能覺之者</l><l><note n="0778006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">唯＝惟【甲】</note><note n="0778006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唯【大】，惟【甲】</note><app n="0778006"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">惟</rdg></app>我能救拔</l>
<lb n="0778a10" ed="T"/><l>永斷生死本</l><l>普處寂滅樂</l></lg>
<lb n="0778a11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0778a1101">即說陀羅尼曰。</p>
<lb n="0778a12" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0778a1201" cb:type="dharani">句利句利帝那憂<note n="0778007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">拙＝杜【甲】＊</note><note n="0778007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">拙【大】＊，杜【甲】＊</note><app n="0778007"><lem wit="【大】">拙</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">杜</rdg></app>憂<app type="star" corresp="#0778007"><lem wit="【大】">拙</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">杜</rdg></app>帝那度呼度呼帝
<lb n="0778a13" ed="T"/>那究吒究吒帝那若<note n="0778008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">蜜＝密【甲】下同</note><note n="0778008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蜜【大】下同，密【甲】下同</note><app n="0778008"><lem wit="【大】">蜜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">密</rdg></app>都若蜜都帝那究吒
<lb n="0778a14" ed="T"/>呼究吒呼帝那憂守憂守帝那耶蜜若耶蜜若
<lb n="0778a15" ed="T"/>帝那度呼吒究吒多薩嚩<note place="inline">二<note n="0778009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">合＋（引）【甲】</note><note n="0778009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">合【大】，合引【甲】</note><app n="0778009"><lem wit="【大】">合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">合引</rdg></app></note><note n="0778010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">訶＋（引）細註【甲】</note><note n="0778010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">訶【大】，訶(引)【甲】</note><app n="0778010"><lem wit="【大】">訶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">訶<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0778a16" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0778a1601">右誦呪三遍。結縷作七結繫脚。是呪能令諸
<lb n="0778a17" ed="T"/>失心者。還得正念。滅婬<app type="star" corresp="#0778004"><lem wit="【大】">慾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">欲</rdg></app>火除我慢結。三
<lb n="0778a18" ed="T"/>毒垢盡自然清<note n="0778011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">涼＝淨【甲】</note><note n="0778011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">涼【大】，淨【甲】</note><app n="0778011"><lem wit="【大】">涼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">淨</rdg></app>。若有精神。<note n="0778012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">沈＝沒【甲】</note><note n="0778012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">沈【大】，沒【甲】</note><app n="0778012"><lem wit="【大】">沈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">沒</rdg></app>在無明重
<lb n="0778a19" ed="T"/>淵之下。久溺生死不得出要。<note n="0778013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">嗚＝鳴【甲】</note><note n="0778013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嗚【大】，鳴【甲】</note><app n="0778013"><lem wit="【大】">嗚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">鳴</rdg></app>呼深可傷。
<lb n="0778a20" ed="T"/>若人心得<note n="0778014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">醒＝惺【甲】</note><note n="0778014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">醒【大】，惺【甲】</note><app n="0778014"><lem wit="【大】">醒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">惺</rdg></app>悟極自厭污。此是凡夫愚下鬼
<lb n="0778a21" ed="T"/>神畜生之所行處。非梵行所宜。非聖人所願。
<lb n="0778a22" ed="T"/>如此之人方可<note n="0778015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">受＝授【甲】</note><note n="0778015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">受【大】，授【甲】</note><app n="0778015"><lem wit="【大】">受</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">授</rdg></app>與此陀羅尼。勿傳矯俗疑
<lb n="0778a23" ed="T"/><note n="0778016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">謗＝豫【甲】</note><note n="0778016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">謗【大】，豫【甲】</note><app n="0778016"><lem wit="【大】">謗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">豫</rdg></app>少信。縱持無<note n="0778017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">驗＝福【甲】</note><note n="0778017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">驗【大】，福【甲】</note><app n="0778017"><lem wit="【大】">驗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">福</rdg></app>即轉退墮。若至誠誦者
<lb n="0778a24" ed="T"/><note n="0778018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（婬）＋慾【甲】</note><note n="0778018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">慾【大】，婬慾【甲】</note><app n="0778018"><lem wit="【大】">慾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">婬慾</rdg></app>火漸<note n="0778019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">盡＝消滅婬欲滅已慢心自滅慢心滅已其心則定其心定心結使都滅【甲】</note><note n="0778019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">盡【大】，消滅婬欲滅已慢心自滅慢心滅已其心則定其心定心結使都滅【甲】</note><app n="0778019"><lem wit="【大】">盡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">消滅婬欲滅已慢心自滅慢心滅已其心則定其心定心結使都滅</rdg></app>。結使滅已心得解脫。心解脫已
<lb n="0778a25" ed="T"/><note n="0778020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">則＝即【甲】</note><note n="0778020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">則【大】，即【甲】</note><app n="0778020"><lem wit="【大】">則</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">即</rdg></app>得道果。是則神力功用誠諦不虛。行此
<lb n="0778a26" ed="T"/>法者斷<note n="0778021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">酒＋（肉）【甲】</note><note n="0778021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">酒【大】，酒肉【甲】</note><app n="0778021"><lem wit="【大】">酒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">酒肉</rdg></app>五辛血食。男子<note n="0778022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔唯用〕－【甲】＊</note><note n="0778022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唯用【大】＊，〔－〕【甲】＊</note><app n="0778022"><lem wit="【大】">唯用</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>九九八十
<lb n="0778a27" ed="T"/>一日。女子<app type="star" corresp="#0778022"><lem wit="【大】">唯用</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>七七四十九日。晝夜六時勤
<lb n="0778a28" ed="T"/>心讀誦。燒沈水白檀香散花。供養十方諸佛。
<lb n="0778a29" ed="T"/>晝三夜三慎勿廢忘。日數未滿餘時之中。獨
<pb n="0778b" xml:id="T20.1178.0778b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0778b01" ed="T"/>處山窟精舍。若聚落<note n="0778023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">即淨室三字甲本作夾註</note><note n="0778023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">即淨室【大】，(即淨室)【甲】</note><app n="0778023"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">即淨室</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><note place="inline">即淨室</note></rdg></app>四向遠人。當深生
<lb n="0778b02" ed="T"/>欣躍自發慶幸。今我遭遇大聖神力。此身宜
<lb n="0778b03" ed="T"/>至佛身。不懼淪溺。如是淨心念念信向。斷諸
<lb n="0778b04" ed="T"/>惡作轉雜言論離間之語。不念名利。如是日
<lb n="0778b05" ed="T"/>數足已。決定解脫其心泰然無復<note n="0778024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">欲＝慾【甲】</note><note n="0778024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">欲【大】，慾【甲】</note><app n="0778024"><lem wit="【大】">欲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">慾</rdg></app><note n="0778025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">慢字次行甲本有文殊滅婬我慢陀羅尼十字</note>慢。</p></cb:div>
</body></text></TEI>